com.example.appraisal.model

Class MainModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.appraisal.model.MainModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataRequestable

    public class MainModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataRequestable
    This structure is the major backend that host the connection to Firebase and many other things. This is a Singleton design pattern and should be called at least once right after the app starts via createInstance()

        public static void createInstance()
        Use this method to create one single instance of the MainModel. If left untouched, its lifetime would persists throughout the whole app. Should be called at least once right after the app starts.
